<div class="dablink">For the ethical doctrine, see <a href="/wiki/Altruism_(ethics)" title="Altruism (ethics)">Altruism (ethics)</a>.</div>
<p><b>Altruism</b> (from Latin: alter: the other) is the <a href="/wiki/Deliberate" title="Deliberate" class="mw-redirect">deliberate</a> pursuit of the interests or <a href="/wiki/Welfare" title="Welfare">welfare</a> of others or the public interest.</p>
